query:
SELECT 
  p.brand,
  c.name as category,
  COUNT(DISTINCT p.id) as product_count
FROM products p
JOIN product_categories pc ON p.id = pc.productId
JOIN categories c ON pc.categoryId = c.id
WHERE c.name IN ('HPLC Columns', 'GC Columns', 'Guard Columns', 'SPE Cartridges', 'Filtration', 'Chromatography Supplies')
GROUP BY p.brand, c.name
ORDER BY p.brand, c.name
LIMIT 50
